全不輸歐洲主流攻擊手的速度為他贏得了不少球迷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211bbc0028586b67a5a5ad0d42121696b9d2bfb9","tid":1801252,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:00:54.000Z","msg":"開場2分29秒！26歲伊朗國腳獲英超處子球，激動地掩面而泣"},{"pid":"e8bd8d50ccf7e811bd9f8e76f869c0ff07e64809","tid":1801252,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"這是26歲的伊朗國腳加盟布萊頓一年多以來的首粒英超進球。收穫個人英超處子球的賈漢巴赫什非常激動，掩面而泣，隊友也紛紛過來擁抱他，如此場面令人動容。賈漢巴赫什也成為第三位在英超取得進球的伊朗球員，前兩位分別是德賈加(富勒姆)和大家熟悉的泰穆里安(博爾頓、富勒姆)。"},{"pid":"1ca3da44cd67609bc270411eb012667027164748","tid":1801252,"uid":34899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"去德甲啦 伊朗人發光發熱之地"},{"pid":"b62b066038ee74c48d5223542f37b1f14727439d","tid":1801252,"uid":95358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37333bf519c534d81fc5cff246c49228942e6f1e","tid":1801252,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"佢個樣唔似伊朗人，似高加索人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T16:04:51.000Z","msg":"中東印度其實都係高加索種"},{"pid":"7eabcbf6b47ab981657fc1975c53f61ec468fed5","tid":1801252,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T09:59:17.000Z","msg":"【英超戰報】伊朗國腳開齋激動到喊 白禮頓兩球淨勝般茅"},{"pid":"6adcebe10591d42ab223d144701448bc57a7d7ff","tid":1801252,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37333bf519c534d81fc5cff246c49228942e6f1e","tid":1801252,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"佢個樣唔似伊朗人，似高加索人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"伊朗咪高加索人其中一個分支"},{"pid":"d945fc664c6b28febcd8763d82b09d50df95b821","tid":1801252,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37333bf519c534d81fc5cff246c492